Use Case: Run Member Reports
Context: A report is sent to all members of ChocAn either automatically on Friday at midnight or manually by the ChocAn Manager.
Actors: ChocAn Manager
Main Success Scenario:
	1.System detects that it is midnight on Friday.
	2.System generates reports for all members that received services from providers.
	3.System sends the reports to members involved via email attachment.
Extensions:
	1a. Manager chooses a member to send a report to.
	1b. System generates a report for that member.
	1c. Use case resumes at step 3.